{"tid":2262500,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"印度議會譴責Twitter將Ladakh列為中國領土不尊重印度主權   Twitter迅速改正中國地圖標記","createTime":"2020-10-29T07:27:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-29T08:09:21.000Z","uid":204533,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a0c36433ec6dff7f67c82ddab04b5289075afd02","tid":2262500,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T07:27:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>印度議會小組星期三（10月28日）指責推特的數據製圖把印度控制的拉達克地區（Ladakh) 列為中國的一部分，說這是不尊重印度主權，儘管之前推特迅速修正了這個錯誤。<br />\n<br />\n拉達克位於喜馬拉雅山印中邊界線，該地長期被捲入印中兩國的地緣政治爭端。今年6月印中在那裡發生了兩國45年來最嚴重的流血衝突，從而使拉達克成為兩國邊境衝突中最為人知的地點。<br />\n<br />\n印度議會聯合委員會星期三審查印度&ldquo;個人數據保護法案&rdquo;（Personal Data Prrotection Bill) 時，一些委員向在場的印度推特主管質問有關推特地理標記的問題。上星期有人發現推特的地理標記把拉達克列為中國的一部分。在場的推特主管隨即做出解釋，並說推特很快就改正了這個錯誤。<br />\n<br />\n但是來自執政黨印度人民黨的委員會主席梅納克什&middot;萊基（ Meenakshi Lekhi) 對路透社說，委員會一致認為推特的解釋不夠充分。<br />\n<br />\n萊基說，推特表示尊重（這個議題的）敏感性，推特的說法不夠充分，&ldquo;這事關印度主權與國家完整&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n印度斯坦時報星期三報導說，<strong><span class=\"red\">萊基還說，把拉達克顯示為中國的一部分，該行為構成刑事犯罪，可導致7年徒刑。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n推特一名女發言人回應萊基的說法稱，推特致力於工作的公開、透明，並將繼續定期與印度政府保持聯繫，以分享及時更新的信息。</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voachinese.com/a/Indian-parliamentary-panel-slams-twitter-China-map-dispute-20201028/5638926.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voachinese.com%2Fa%2FIndian-parliamentary-panel-slams-twitter-China-map-dispute-20201028%2F5638926.html&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5Kiiq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=b08c23b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.voachinese.com/a/Indian-parliamentary-panel-slams-twitter-China-map-dispute-20201028/5638926.html</a>"},{"pid":"fe1036107a3785dc780a5cf4b3d5758f87f09050","tid":2262500,"uid":66049,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T07:29:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />專恰trump trump"},{"pid":"7e51de8f84d74dfdf165419a785bd56d6d1f9c91","tid":2262500,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T07:29:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f235b46e8d5d9b9e98398714409707b265372fb","tid":2262500,"uid":14494,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T07:29:37.000Z","msg":"一個印度<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4294bdb502eced057a5dd5b905a0f178d97293fa","tid":2262500,"uid":184726,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T07:38:40.000Z","msg":"只有野蠻先可以同野蠻對抗<br />\n靠歐美班左膠偽君子死撚得"},{"pid":"926fd461fc029efa27fea41c0ccef5f0b697f39a","tid":2262500,"uid":91397,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T07:39:53.000Z","msg":"印度佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e2296b2fcb994b0fb63cf455340e7eb7c66b968","tid":2262500,"uid":8308,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T07:46:17.000Z","msg":"好彩亞洲有印度佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係支共真係打橫行冇人理"},{"pid":"d8c71bc3d0a584d8b6bbfd0b70ad5867899fb4e9","tid":2262500,"uid":57376,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T07:50:39.000Z","msg":"大家都係13憶市場<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac42b142e743b4e31de2e9f65199f7c73be3cb58","tid":2262500,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T07:53:37.000Z","msg":"Chitter"},{"pid":"ae2d087c2c18bc4296c4cd37fe4992dc53281610","tid":2262500,"uid":225192,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d8c71bc3d0a584d8b6bbfd0b70ad5867899fb4e9","tid":2262500,"u